modName: Aya - Nord or Ashen female Level 2 Save File
summary: Aya is a Black haired female. Now available as Nord but with the same great look as the Ashen version
descriptionHtml:
To have her look exactly as in the image you will need to be using the following fantastic mods -

   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/8583]For Ashen Race[/url] or [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/19666]Fair skin mod if using Nord file[/url]
   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url]
   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/4869]Covereyes[/url]
   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2812]Better Females by Bella[/url]
   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168]ApachiiSkyHair[/url]
   [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/3563]seamless UNP and Coverwomen Look_3[/url]

Optional for over all Skyrim visual boost (please note there are alot of great ENB options would advise looking into them) -

[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/30158]K ENB[/url]

All of the above mods make the game so much better and the modders that made them put in a massive amount of work - please endorse them if you use and like what they do.

Lastly I hope you enjoy playing as this character -  if you have questions or problems just let me know in comments and Ill try and assist with load order etc.
author: Alstar80
